Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是隻沒教養的貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖魔?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鬼斬役十二家之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神宮寺家的女兒兼繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖惠澄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神宮寺玖惠澄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼斬役
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.72,0:00:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我之外鬼斬役…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好驚訝的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起消滅妖魔的命運…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:00:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑我和你的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.36,0:01:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓給我滾一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就揮舞著爪子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是傷到我這個漂亮的臉蛋的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳該如何賠我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓就給我像隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.71,0:01:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縮在牆角才適合妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.44,0:01:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次遇見我的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛子的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在稍微能了解到一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河優人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不需要再和那些醜惡的妖魔相處下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為之後你將會有我陪在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
